               <desc xml:id="abstract-en-78" xml:lang="en">A city of Mesopotamia, the capital of the ancient kingdom of Osrhoene, modern Urfa.</desc>
               <desc xml:lang="en">
                  <quote source="#bib78-1">183. Edessa</quote>
               </desc>
               <desc xml:lang="syr-Syrj">
                  <quote source="#bib78-3">ܡܕܺܝܢܬܐ ܗܳܝ ܛܒܝܒܬܳܐ ܠܡܰܕܢܚܳܐ ܕܚܳܠܳܒ ܚܰܡܫܳܐ ܝܰܘܡ̈ܝܢ ܘܡܶܫܬܰܡܗܐ ܝܰܘܡܳܢ ܐܘܪܦܰܗ̈</quote>
               </desc>
               <desc xml:lang="ar">
                  <quote source="#bib78-4">مدينة مشهورة خمسة ايام عن حلب شرقا وتسمى اليوم اورفه.</quote>
               </desc>
               <desc xml:lang="en">
                  <quote source="#bib78-5">a famous city, five day journey eastward from Aleppo, now called Urfa.</quote>
               </desc>
